      • getBestTurnFromChildren

        public int getBestTurnFromChildren()
        Determines the best possible turn of all of this nodes children by determining the turn with the highest score. If there is more than one turn with the highest score, a turn will be picked by random among the best turns.
        Returns:
        The child index with the best turn
